<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Room 1: The Toxicology Lab</title>
    <style>
        body, html { margin: 0; padding: 0; height: 100%; overflow: hidden; font-family: sans-serif; }
        .room { 
            position: relative; width: 100vw; height: 100vh; 
            /* Using a high-quality lab photo for the search */
            background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1582719471384-894fbb16e074?q=80&w=2000') no-repeat center center; 
            background-size: cover; 
        }
        /* THE HIDDEN TARGET: The medical file on the desk. 
           Change background to 0.0 to make it truly invisible! */
        .hotspot { 
            position: absolute; cursor: pointer; 
            top: 55%; left: 42%; width: 100px; height: 80px; 
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15); 
            border: 1px dashed white;
        }
        .modal { display: none; position: fixed; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); background: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 0 50px #000; z-index: 100; max-width: 400px; text-align: center; }
        .overlay { display: none; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.8); z-index: 90; }
        input { padding: 10px; width: 80%; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 5px; margin: 10px 0; text-transform: uppercase; }
        button { background: #d9534f; color: white; border: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="room">
        <div style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7); color: white; padding: 15px; position: absolute; top: 10px; left: 10px; border-radius: 5px;">
            <h3>📍 MISSION 1: THE SEARCH</h3>
            <p>A new sedative is contaminating the 2026 supply. Search the room for the <strong>Tox Report</strong> to find its name.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hotspot" onclick="showClue()"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="overlay" id="overlay"></div>
    <div class="modal" id="clueModal">
        <h2>📂 TOXICOLOGY ALERT</h2>
        <p><strong>April 2026 Update:</strong> Xylazine is being replaced by <strong>Medetomidine</strong>—a veterinary sedative 100x more potent. It causes dangerously low heart rates.</p>
        <hr>
        <p><strong>PUZZLE:</strong> Type the name of this new sedative to verify the evidence.</p>
        <input type="text" id="answer" placeholder="TYPE NAME HERE...">
        <br>
        <button onclick="checkAnswer()">VERIFY EVIDENCE</button>
        <div id="success" style="display:none; margin-top:20px; color:green; font-weight:bold;">
            <p>✅ CORRECT. Clue Word 1: "VIGILANCE"</p>
            <p><a href="room2.html" style="color:blue; text-decoration: underline;">GO TO ROOM 2 &rarr;</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function showClue() { 
            document.getElementById('clueModal').style.display = 'block'; 
            document.getElementById('overlay').style.display = 'block'; 
        }
        function checkAnswer() {
            if (document.getElementById('answer').value.toUpperCase().trim() === 'MEDETOMIDINE') {
                document.getElementById('success').style.display = 'block';
            } else { alert("Incorrect! Look closely at the report."); }
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
